entries.title_d: Your radar shows a Rebel scout fighter. This confirms that the route has been compromised but the commander wants you to eliminate the Rebel.
entries.title: Yavin system: Scouts spotted!
entries.split_quest_alert: Imperial Space Station: < The scout must have alerted his friends, they are heading your way! >
entries.complete: Imperial Space Station: < Good job! This confirms it though, we need to change our routes immediately. Try to find more of them Rebel lowlifes! >
